Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.90,0:00:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.74,0:00:19.65,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Newdays 開始的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.71,0:00:23.91,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,給世界一個吻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.99,0:00:25.51,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Blowing in thewind
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.59,0:00:32.25,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,把一點點的勇氣和愛放進口袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.43,0:00:41.03,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,l wish如果我有翅膀的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.64,0:00:50.17,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,不管悲傷、過去還是不安 都能夠飛越
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.25,0:00:51.91,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,OhYeah！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.98,0:00:56.94,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有失去什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.72,0:01:00.78,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemyway！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.86,0:01:03.59,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,想用這掌心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.66,0:01:07.29,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,抓住奇蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.76,0:01:16.26,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,朝向無盡的天空和大地 以及未來旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.74,0:01:19.94,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,剛長出的翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.01,0:01:23.17,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh！ 一定 一定 一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.24,0:01:24.37,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.45,0:01:28.35,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,展現光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.85,0:01:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要快點離開這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.35,0:01:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子已經曝光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.62,0:01:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長相大概也被看見了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.39,0:01:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要開門？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.49,0:01:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算不開他也會破門而入的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.96,0:01:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他現在應該在跟支援部隊聯繫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.13,0:01:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會合之後馬上就會攻進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.74,0:01:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡已經不能再待下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.44,0:01:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.71,0:01:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.08,0:02:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.09,0:02:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動作快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.06,0:02:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開門，我們是王國軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.69,0:02:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點開門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.89,0:02:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一，二...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.97,0:02:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是什麼地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.20,0:02:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.31,0:02:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很久以前就有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.44,0:02:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以前就知道這個地方了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.91,0:02:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.15,0:02:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#18 小巷裡的哀歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.36,0:02:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.76,0:02:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是小劇場啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.70,0:02:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃避到虛構世界的娛樂設施嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.97,0:02:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是詩音的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.47,0:02:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該會真心感到高興吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.51,0:03:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.58,0:03:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天也有人問了同一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.28,0:03:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問說有沒有金髮藍眼的小姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.72,0:03:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個小姑娘做了什麼壞事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.49,0:03:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.06,0:03:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.09,0:03:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,街上還有人在巡邏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.93,0:03:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就表示還沒被王國軍帶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.56,0:03:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...到底去哪裡了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.77,0:03:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.47,0:03:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說那個年輕人\N看起來不是也挺能幹的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.91,0:03:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.47,0:03:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之，他們有可能再回到這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.31,0:03:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再等看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.02,0:03:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉貝拉姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.06,0:03:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉貝拉姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.29,0:03:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼在這種地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.56,0:03:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明明把你託給旅館的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.36,0:03:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.10,0:03:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了相關人員之外禁止進入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.93,0:04:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的話快滾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.14,0:04:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這匹馬，是我的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.37,0:04:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.44,0:04:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.38,0:04:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫找不到？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.22,0:04:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們徵收王都內飼主不明的馬匹\N已經封住了他們的機動能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.89,0:04:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巡邏的人數也加倍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.13,0:04:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們一定躲在某個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.63,0:04:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好，無論如何都要找到他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.70,0:04:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是攸關王國的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.60,0:04:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.44,0:04:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，這下麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.34,0:04:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到連我和薇妮雅小姐\N都被通緝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.88,0:04:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且剛剛好像也有人\N來問關於金髮藍眼小姑娘的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.45,0:04:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲在這裡說不定很快就會被找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.52,0:04:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之得儘快離開王都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.12,0:04:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...我還是不太懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.23,0:05:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我是廢棄公主\N我為什麼非逃不可呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.20,0:05:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.63,0:05:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.00,0:05:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是公主嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.90,0:05:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼非抓我不可呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.17,0:05:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為對王國來說妳是危險人物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.34,0:05:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.41,0:05:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底哪裡危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.54,0:05:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.91,0:05:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，瑪烏傑魯教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.85,0:05:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直宣稱廢棄公主\N會為世界帶來災難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.85,0:05:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我還留在軍中\N現在應該也在找妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.72,0:05:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你曾經是軍人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.56,0:05:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.30,0:05:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把蛋夾走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.17,0:05:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛋的話不是還有很多顆嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.34,0:05:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一顆煮得剛剛好\N我剛剛正想夾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.21,0:05:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了，去夾別的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.34,0:05:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是還沒放到嘴裡嗎\N給我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.18,0:05:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.15,0:05:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...帕希菲卡小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.95,0:05:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕美拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕美拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.18,0:05:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳不嫌棄我這顆的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.58,0:05:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那顆太早夾起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.82,0:06:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要等表面變得更深色一點才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.26,0:06:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說把那顆給我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.19,0:06:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.16,0:06:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玉米烤好了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.16,0:06:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基塔夫先生，真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.13,0:06:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不但讓我們躲在這裡\N還請我們吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.53,0:06:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.10,0:06:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.57,0:06:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過，太吵的話\N會被團長罵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.37,0:06:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.84,0:06:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.97,0:06:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.94,0:06:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我安靜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯，你到底是怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.91,0:06:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明找到廢棄公主的藏身之處\N為什麼不採取行動？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.25,0:06:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家稍安勿躁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.45,0:06:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小克里一定有什麼想法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.99,0:06:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯，你打算怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.76,0:06:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.93,0:06:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，老實說我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.96,0:06:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把廢棄公主交給王國\N到底是不是正確的決定...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.10,0:06:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這樣下去\N我們執拗之矢就要被迫解散了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.14,0:06:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們如果離開這裡\N會有什麼下場呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.75,0:07:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭啦，薩頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.38,0:07:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.62,0:07:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.69,0:07:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然全國的人都想殺我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.52,0:07:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算說要逃\N那要逃到哪裡才算安全呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.16,0:07:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的有安全的地方嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.50,0:07:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.73,0:07:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到鄰國基亞特帝國去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.90,0:07:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡的話\N就不必擔心被王國軍追殺了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.37,0:07:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前也就算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.14,0:07:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王都外海發生奈落事件之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.64,0:07:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家跟基亞特\N已經陷入了緊張狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.61,0:07:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在離開王國反而更危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.75,0:07:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.35,0:07:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到聖都葛林德怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.79,0:07:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說的葛林德...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.06,0:07:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會是瑪烏傑魯教的總部吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.53,0:07:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然位於萊邦王國境內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.89,0:07:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻只有那邊是完全的獨立自治區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是王國軍的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.40,0:07:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也只能攜帶非常有限的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.34,0:08:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王國軍應該也不會想到\N廢棄公主竟然會逃到葛林德去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.94,0:08:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說聖都那邊有\N瑪烏傑魯直屬的戰鬥部隊肅清使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.68,0:08:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是比起繼續跟整個王國軍為敵\N要好多了，不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.06,0:08:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個，大家...我覺得很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.66,0:08:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我還是不太懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.76,0:08:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是大家都是因為我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.70,0:08:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.47,0:08:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒辦法的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.40,0:08:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情都已經到了這個地步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.74,0:08:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.57,0:08:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過\N拉蔻兒小姐他們應該也很擔心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.14,0:08:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我們一起消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.48,0:08:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位可怕的大姊也在王都啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.25,0:08:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.55,0:08:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前在小攤子遇到的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.22,0:08:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少應該問一下\N他們住在哪一間旅館才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.92,0:08:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以稍微延後一點出發嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.63,0:08:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了，我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.53,0:08:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再拖拖拉拉下去\N大家都會被抓走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.93,0:09:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果遇到大姊，我會跟她說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.00,0:09:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣我們都需要馬匹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.24,0:09:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,徒步是行不通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.84,0:09:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是照雷歐先生所說\N警備不是很嚴密嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.68,0:09:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣的守備都會有破綻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.08,0:09:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也贊成去搶馬匹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.98,0:09:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，要是在半路上被發現了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.58,0:09:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.75,0:09:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要喬裝改扮一下？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.52,0:09:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是這個最好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.06,0:09:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薇妮雅絕對很適合\N穿這種大膽的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.89,0:09:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.64,0:09:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.97,0:09:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.24,0:09:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是有話想說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.31,0:09:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說\N帕美拉小姐也是很重要的人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.05,0:09:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要到即使犧牲生命也想保護她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.22,0:09:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.85,0:09:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在不是為了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.39,0:09:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保護被全國人民追殺的那個人\N才在這裡的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.13,0:10:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說起來也沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.83,0:10:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概像是條件反射吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.33,0:10:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為工作時我老是放走\N被人追殺或是惹了麻煩的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.64,0:10:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只因為這樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.71,0:10:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你又是為了什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.91,0:10:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.85,0:10:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你重視她到\N即使拋棄自己重要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.08,0:10:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也想要保護她是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.92,0:10:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你是不是見習的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.06,0:10:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，你已經無法成為騎士了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.36,0:10:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.79,0:10:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還問為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.26,0:10:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,砍下廢棄公主的頭帶回去\N才是你本來的職責，不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.93,0:10:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只會砍殺才算是騎士嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.00,0:10:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不認為是那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.47,0:10:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.81,0:10:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.85,0:10:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.52,0:10:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.59,0:10:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.72,0:11:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.62,0:11:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說幾句中聽的話嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.36,0:11:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒...好好看喔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.73,0:11:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了，受不了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.76,0:11:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你看了也是白看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.83,0:11:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.37,0:11:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊，在找喬裝用的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.30,0:11:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個的已經決定好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.38,0:11:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.21,0:11:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妝是不是淡了點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.65,0:11:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.47,0:11:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.97,0:11:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說好聽話\N老實說真的很適合你耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.24,0:11:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你們佩服我\N我也不會高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.18,0:11:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，女孩子可不會說\N那麼粗魯的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.88,0:12:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳根本沒資格說別人，不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.45,0:12:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖聽淑女的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.75,0:12:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳算是淑女嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.09,0:12:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.49,0:12:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.00,0:12:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.27,0:12:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們去搶馬匹回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.08,0:12:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩位請在這裡稍等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.91,0:12:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不穿女裝去嗎？真是不好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.71,0:12:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿那種東西哪有辦法動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.88,0:12:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以受傷，要安全回來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.49,0:12:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道，都說不必擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.19,0:12:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.36,0:12:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是受傷我們不就麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.13,0:12:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還得幫你包紮傷口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.86,0:12:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.30,0:12:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之，連一點擦傷都不可以有喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.67,0:12:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是是，公主殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.17,0:12:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛死人了，妳這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.10,0:12:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐先生也要加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.77,0:12:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.88,0:13:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...帕美拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.68,0:13:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.12,0:13:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.85,0:13:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在看起來不是很可靠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.89,0:13:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是想保護妳的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.79,0:13:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會輸給任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.16,0:13:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.47,0:13:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.48,0:13:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐先生剛剛真帥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.59,0:13:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了我一大跳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.02,0:13:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然對我說那種話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.42,0:13:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳覺得如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.83,0:13:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對雷歐先生的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.50,0:13:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的心意我是很高興啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.36,0:13:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他看起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.30,0:14:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不覺得有種公子哥兒的感覺嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.77,0:14:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他是貴族嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.64,0:14:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.11,0:14:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是覺得他是個好人啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.61,0:14:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳比較喜歡弗雷先生嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.78,0:14:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那麼說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.55,0:14:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.38,0:14:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.72,0:14:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對那傢伙也說不上是\N喜歡還是討厭...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.92,0:14:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然哪一匹都無所謂\N不過要找看起來跑得快的下手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.83,0:14:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我已經決定好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.36,0:14:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.23,0:14:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉貝拉姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.03,0:14:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你的馬啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.87,0:14:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然不能輕鬆的回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.48,0:14:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.81,0:14:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.41,0:14:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.10,0:15:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說妳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.43,0:15:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣只會讓我看起來像個傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.47,0:15:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來撐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.34,0:15:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫無意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.77,0:15:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們秩序守護者的身體\N就算淋濕了也不會有任何問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.68,0:15:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起撐就對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.75,0:15:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你淋濕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.09,0:15:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續這種狀態的話\N你的體溫會下降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.69,0:15:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.41,0:15:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.35,0:15:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓住這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.95,0:15:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們的速度比較快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.45,0:15:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會被追上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.72,0:15:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.55,0:16:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果被追上就沒有意義了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.16,0:16:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.29,0:16:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我隨後就跟上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.46,0:16:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就這樣告訴帕美拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.96,0:16:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡由我來擋住他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.76,0:16:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.76,0:16:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.10,0:16:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保護公主殿下\N不正是騎士的責任嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.17,0:16:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.90,0:16:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我，是誰說要保護帕美拉的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.84,0:16:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.57,0:16:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聲音太小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.71,0:16:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有自信嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.71,0:16:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.68,0:16:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就去保護她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.68,0:16:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.43,0:16:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.56,0:16:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.05,0:17:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕美拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.92,0:17:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快騎上來，薇妮雅小姐也快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.26,0:17:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.76,0:17:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他隨後一定會跟上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.61,0:18:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.84,0:18:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明知跟王國作對會有什麼下場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.02,0:18:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你還要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.01,0:18:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.75,0:18:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.92,0:18:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.76,0:19:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是想去某個地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.16,0:19:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.53,0:19:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這男人的生命反應已經消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.10,0:19:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管這傢伙想去哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.04,0:19:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都已經沒必要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.34,0:19:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果沒有人告訴他\N就算想去也去不了的事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.98,0:19:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是無法安息的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.20,0:20:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐波爾特先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.14,0:20:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.27,0:20:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼從剛才開始\N你就不敢看我的眼睛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.94,0:20:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷會來吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.32,0:20:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要回弗雷那裡去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.39,0:20:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕美拉小姐，不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.39,0:20:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.49,0:20:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.14,0:20:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.13,0:21:17.93,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,滋潤大地的雨水靜靜地飄下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.01,0:21:23.31,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,落在很遠很遠的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.38,0:21:30.68,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,將這愛的雨滴獻給 某個等待已久的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.75,0:21:36.25,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,清晨的微風吹過沾有雨滴的臉龐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.32,0:21:41.32,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,現在你感覺到什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.40,0:21:44.63,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,這雨滴有著明白的含意 比一切都還要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.70,0:21:49.57,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,就在那唯一的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.64,0:21:56.20,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,停駐在追趕著的雲影下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.28,0:21:59.54,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,在這心靈的旅程中想要找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.61,0:22:02.88,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,不管到哪裡不管到哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.95,0:22:09.48,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天會再聽到熟悉的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.56,0:22:16.22,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,船將會啟航啟航 船會航行到哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.30,0:22:21.53,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯要相信廣闊的世界 到未知的海洋的盡頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.60,0:22:28.77,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,你要前往遠方然後奔向未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.74,0:22:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被克里斯他們抓到的帕希菲卡\N被關進了王城的地下牢房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.41,0:22:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡不但潮濕多灰塵，且又暗又窄\N還臭到讓人想吐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.02,0:22:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡感到孤單又不安\N不過，隔壁牢房好像還關著其他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.56,0:22:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人為什麼會被關在牢裡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.72,0:22:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄公主 下一回\N「母親嘆息的無言歌」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.09,0:22:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待